agent-persona-worker - Agent Persona Worker

USAGE:
    agent-persona-worker <agent-persona>

DESCRIPTION:
    Execute agent task with specific persona configuration.
    Creates job and delegates to agent-worker for execution.

ARGUMENTS:
    agent-persona
        Agent persona configuration to use (required)

EXAMPLES:
    agent-persona-worker developer
    agent-persona-worker tester
    agent-persona-worker analyst
